{"type": "article", "id": 48707, "title": "挂着的雪花装饰，仔细看有一幢幢标志建筑物｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-12-28T23:26:01Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 46648, "name": "Allies and Morrison"}, {"id": 45567, "name": "Super Local"}, {"id": 41284, "name": "蔡烈超"}, {"id": 46649, "name": "Toshihiro Otomo"}, {"id": 29485, "name": "Alain Gilles"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 66, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171229072552qKZERhT26lacPt1Y.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #303030; -webkit-text-stroke: #303030} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: #333333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s4 {font-kerning: none; color: #303030; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #303030} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s6 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #000000} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} span.s8 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>HANA - Flower Colored Pencils by Toshihiro Otomo</h3><p>日本设计公司 TRINUS 与设计师 Toshihiro Otomo 将五种日本最具代表性的花卉变成系列花色铅笔，包括粉色的樱花、绿色的常盘绿、黄色的蒲公英、红色的红梅以及蓝色的桔梗。通过改变铅笔轮廓，每当用户削铅笔时，铅笔屑便会变成花朵模样，像是随风掉落的花瓣，充满诗意。</p><p>时值冬季，TRINUS 还推出了三种颜色的雪花主题铅笔，以雪花的六角结晶设计造型，包含白色、银色及金色三种选择，混合着闪闪发光的小颗粒在里头。这些花色铅笔全部都是由回收废纸材料制成，兼具环保性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232853TBa4bixYJ5v0sFDH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.749000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232751AbImauMfe9wkvDgl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656250\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712282327518y6CoefzBuhNOmIK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646126\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232751pScYNRzU1Ve3QA9g.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.593519\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232752awWcRQPksMGSO1iK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232752wWRJgESKeTPXp8qQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Care Collection by Super Local</h3><p>荷兰设计工作室 Super Local 与马拉维工匠合作开发了一系列可以在当地生产的经济实惠的医院护理产品。这一系列包括医院病床、手术台、手推车、房间隔断、输液架、床上用桌和洗衣手推车等等，每一件作品都在今年的荷兰设计周中展出。</p><p>因为进口医疗设备成本太高的缘故，马拉维当地医院不得不使用破旧的设备。为了回应这个问题， Super Local 看到了开发一系列医院产品的机会，这些产品可以通过现成的材料和技术在当地制造。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232703u3T5FRibDHUYASKg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232704qRn2xIbDYBJsiW1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232706hYwrx7IcPUEy9Cmb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232706ngDhxcoK46kmwBdJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2017122823270878lROwyzFbQAeCi1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232711J78hM3HNid9pTe45.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lio by Margaux Reynolds, Jikke van Giffen, Skyler Coppenrath, and Alberto Esses</h3><p>老龄化越来越严重，现阶段老人的生活面临着极大的不便。洛杉矶艺术设计学院的学生们设计了一款名为 Lio 的老人学步车。比起现有设备，这款学步车的特点在于它的稳定性更高，轻便容易折叠，前轮比后轮要大，使它能够更轻松地驶过粗糙的地面和上下坡，这个车还有一个电动辅助制动系统，可以让老人坐下来休息时确保刹车的安全性。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228232958scjKQVNz7WwxyvTD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.605136\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233001kjze2ntPlOfh0pQc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.601926\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233001Xa8cRPSzNQCbO1uZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597134\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233003RCfDozY7LPTviGOh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.603560\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Architecture “Snowflakes” by  Allies and Morrison </h3><p>伦敦建筑公司 Allies and Morrison 在他们的办公室中挂出了一系列雪花片装饰，均是以来自世界各地的著名建筑结构为灵感设计的。这一系列作品由员工 Maria Spada 创造，是针对设计办公室季节性装饰品的内部竞赛给出的解决方案。</p><p>她将独特和精致的雪花图案与建筑平面图的外观结合起来，既有世界知名的建筑作品，亦有可能只有当地人才知晓的隐秘去处。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233048Ioy9XZ25JNqHVF0z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233049nN2vAmXSlxCP8U6y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233049VtCjTmoY9Zdu0SyJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712282330523lsYVEojPBagKyzm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.771605\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233053wceIJh62dGBlUW3X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201712282330533mkvXQ9w7G5tiqoJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Totem-like Side Tables by Alain Gilles</h3><p>这是布鲁塞尔设计师 Alain Gilles 为意大利品牌 Bonaldo 设计的边桌。设计师将不同的形状堆叠起来，形成了这一系列图腾样式的边桌，并由一个轻质的软木底座支撑，与大多数选择传统坚实底座的桌子区隔开来。每个边桌的组装方式不同，用 Gilles 的话说，这些组件就像是“儿童游戏”。软木和木材看似有联系，却又是两种表面完全不同的材料，碰撞在一起的感觉倒也不赖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233119ylfqnmhYMtcxIuF1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233121SKIwm0LDnpEP4Xqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.347716\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233123lKHxFtbIRZYezXio.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.254653\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233124oNG4ArWPmnsDTCiO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.173435\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233124WZRrEXTH2faNAOGU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Ink 砚石首饰盒 by 蔡烈超</h3><p>砚石是中国特有的石材，且由于材料出处为文房用具，气质沉稳细腻。设计师试图发掘其细腻触感与不可复制的自然纹理，拓展其运用范围，使之更融入生活。Ink 砚石首饰盒，呈几何胶囊形，顶盖分为镂槽盖及把手盖共两款。把手的突起与镂槽都可影响视觉上的光影关系，丰富层次。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233205V9Wpbtfe4EkMYB0K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233205DIaSs56eb7Or2vny.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233205d2H3T4lGNren9Eif.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233206WdLCga6Xi4KM9hxe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.712695\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233206G6nCLYUZ0sBzFcEu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171228233206EKLCu1p9ltBjFrdo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}